{"tid":1211774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輿論戰好緊要，政府一定會將造成社會上任何不便矛頭指向示威者","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T17:31:14.000Z","uid":37528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f04b81dc66e8a2b45e869bf8a7ef8dc9d4a2f5d","tid":1211774,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"今日睇柒婆就知，講到自己幾好，幾為香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地就會企係道德高地指責示威者，然後有部分人就會耳濡目染之下信個政府<br />\n(香港返工大個天，我間on9公司今日都出email話9:15要返到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n所以更加要將矛頭指向政府，社會發生咁多野係佢地一手造成<br />\n一百萬人和平遊行，佢地唔聽<br />\n佔領，佢地想殺人唔款<br />\n所以先唯有呢個方法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記著將矛頭指番佢地。</span></span>盡量唔好同普通市民嘈，暫時唔係個個都可以放下身段一齊罷工。難得今次多人對政府反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7180e31bc0fc46cd64c52846ced5841748b155","tid":1211774,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ccf84c91f6b179ec9af04ea279bf80c7029c02","tid":1211774,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"對面有CCTVB 你係香港本土輿論戰好難打<br />\n外國就當然有用<br />\n加上香港高度道德潔癖 你點玩<br />\n你只係衝擊 成班中高收入人士就已經屌9你啦"}]}